explanation: Iterate over every subarray start index l, then extend rightwards while maintaining the GCD of the current subarray and a DP array that tracks the best GCD achievable with j doubles used so far. For each new element, either leave it or double it (if j < k) and update the GCD accordingly. The maximum score is updated on the fly.

